From: Omar Ramadan <omar@blockcast.net>
Date: 2026-06-18
Subject: [PATCH] amt: in-tree Blockcast v6 relay driver for linux-6.18.34

Replaces vanilla linux-6.18.34 drivers/net/amt.c + include/net/amt.h +
include/uapi/linux/amt.h with Blockcast's modified AMT relay driver
(linux-amt, 6.18-native). Built in-tree via CONFIG_AMT=m so the kernel
auto-signs amt.ko with its own trusted build key (CONFIG_MODULE_SIG_ALL),
loads under module.sig_enforce=1, and the struct module ABI matches the
running kernel by construction (no vanilla-vs-pkgs 0x4c0/0x500 drift).

Generated against the exact linux-6.18.34 tarball kernel-prepare fetches.

Signed-off-by: Omar Ramadan <omar@blockcast.net>
---
